location.fullValue: San Sebastian Loft Plan, K. Hovnanian's® Four Seasons at Lakes of Cane Bay

data.description: Welcome home to this open and light filled 3 bedroom, 3 bath popular Athens Loft with extended owner's suite, sunroom and screened porch in the coveted Four Seasons at the Lakes of Cane Bay. Enjoy one story living with 2nd floor loft flex space and a custom designed outdoor oasis. Why wait for new construction, when this move-in ready home has so many upgrades and features...along with being in the established section of Four Seasons with mature trees and plantings. You'll love the stone front, charming front porch, and custom pavers which exude curb appeal.The entry hall opens to a bright and inviting living space. On the right is a sunny guest bedroom and full bath. To the left is a drop zone with custom cabinets and entry to the upgraded garage with epoxy flooring, Saferackoverhead storage and wall shelving.   The open concept living space includes a gourmet kitchen with large island and plenty of room for counter seating, a recently installed GE gas range with convection oven and LG refrigerator, pantry, granite counters and a custom marble tile backsplash. The adjacent dining, sitting and family rooms are ideal for relaxation and entertaining.  The family room leads to the screened porch with epoxy floor and shades to block the sun. Off the screened porch is an extensive custom paver patio featuring a natural gas firepit surrounded by Adirondack chairs. There is plenty of room for additional seating, dining and cooking on your gas grill that can be connected directly to natural gas. Beyond the patio is a professionally landscaped, lighted and fenced backyard.  The spacious owner's suite includes an added sitting area, a luxurious bathroom with oversized shower, double vanity and private water closet. The extra-large walk-in closet conveniently connects to the laundry room with custom cabinetry and utility sink, which also has access to the drop zone off the entry hall. The Samsung washer and dryer will convey with home.  From the entry hall you will find stairs to the 2nd floor loft which includes an open space with built-ins, desk and plenty of storage. This large space is multi-functional...can be used for office, work-out, secondary living space or guest suite and leads to the third bedroom with full bath.  This home features so many desirable upgrades: Generac generator, whole house surge protector, 6 Hunter ceiling fans with remotes as well as ceiling fans with remotes on screened porch, additional insulation blown into attic and front storm door with retractable screen.   Four Seasons is situated on a beautiful 300+ acre lake, perfect for kayaking, fishing & canoeing. Ride your golf cart to the amenities center which has 3 saltwater pools, billiards room, exercise room, yoga, pickleball/bocce/tennis courts and lots of clubs... no shortage of things to do or people to meet!
